regen.absent_element: removal or de-escalation of contact tracing for individuals no longer at risk
regen.new_specification: The system shall allow for the removal or de-escalation of contact tracing for individuals who are no longer at risk, and update associated records and work lists accordingly.

regen.absent_element: mechanism for handling duplicate or conflicting contact information
regen.new_specification: The system shall have a mechanism to handle duplicate or conflicting contact information, ensuring data consistency and accuracy across all linked contacts and cases.

regen.new_specification: The system shall allow for the removal of associations between investigation subjects and exposure contacts when necessary.
